      • partyToBeSeated

        protected boolean partyToBeSeated(Party p)
                           throws java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException,
                                  javax.naming.SizeLimitExceededException
        Checks if Party's name exists in the system, if there is an empty table that will fit them or if they are too large to be seated in the restaurant
        Parameters:
        p - Party passed to check if Name exists in the system, if there is an empty table that will fit them, or if they are too large to be seated in the restaurant
        Returns:
        Returns true if can be seated.
        Throws:
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - If the party's name exists in the system.
        javax.naming.SizeLimitExceededException - If Party's size is too big.
